            "title": "停車爆糾紛 四川漢持生果刀刺死59歲男被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"因停車爆糾紛，四川一名男子持生果刀刺死59歲男子被捕。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/bb26776074ccea6a30b472aa455f16c1/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250516/_2025051613280387097.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">因停車爆糾紛，四川一名男子持生果刀刺死59歲男子被捕。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>四川省內江市東興區錦繡巷16日早上8時10分許發生一宗因車輛停放糾紛引發的持刀傷人致死案件。\n\n</p>\n<p>據內江市公安局東興區分局，2025年5月16日早上8時10分許，東興區錦繡巷發生一宗因車輛停放引發的持刀傷人案，嫌疑人楊某全用水果刀將被害人隆某華（男，59歲）刺傷，經醫務人員搶救無效死亡。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3455888/\">廣州南站35歲男持水果刀傷人　一名傷者送院</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"網傳影片，事發後多人現場圍觀。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/06425c165d5c107735d31a248075e7d5/2025-05/vlcsnap-2025-05-16-13h12m57s552.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網傳影片，事發後多人現場圍觀。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"警方通報。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cfe9bf7eb92b202bd8573e7d1153f96f/2025-05/Clipboard27_4.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方通報。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>案件發生後，公安機關迅速趕赴現場開展調查處置工作。目前，嫌疑人楊某全已被抓獲，案件正在偵辦中。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
